---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Expertise | Alpine Drywall (Calgary) Ltd." description="Steel stud framing, drywall and finishing, acoustical ceilings, and tenant improvements for Calgary's commercial and institutional projects." active="expertise" canonical="https://alpinedrywallcalgary.com/expertise.html">
  <main>
    <section class="page-hero">
      <div class="wrap">
        <span class="eyebrow">Our Expertise</span>
        <h1>Trades, executed cleanly.</h1>
        <p class="lead">We focus on what we do best, so the rest of your trades can do the same.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="framing">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="split">
          <div class="img-frame"><img src="/assets/images/steel-stud-framing-calgary-commercial.jpg" alt="Steel stud framing on a Calgary commercial site" loading="lazy" /></div>
          <div>
            <span class="eyebrow">Steel Stud Framing</span>
            <h2>Square walls, on schedule.</h2>
            <p>Metal stud and track systems for office, retail, healthcare, education, and institutional builds. We work to your engineer's drawings, coordinate with the trades stacking behind us, and frame for the finishes your spec calls for.</p>
            <ul class="checklist">
              <li>Light gauge and heavy gauge framing systems</li>
              <li>Shaft walls and area separation assemblies</li>
              <li>Fire-rated and acoustic-rated wall types</li>
              <li>Soffits, bulkheads, and complex ceiling framing</li>
              <li>Coordination with mechanical and electrical rough-in</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="drywall" class="section-dark">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="split split-reverse">
          <div class="img-frame"><img src="/assets/images/suspended-ceiling-installation-calgary-office.jpg" alt="Drywall and ceiling installation in a Calgary office" loading="lazy" /></div>
          <div>
            <span class="eyebrow">Drywall &amp; Finishing</span>
            <h2>Board, taped, painted-ready.</h2>
            <p>From standard 5/8" gypsum to abuse-resistant and moisture-resistant board, we hang it tight, tape it clean, and finish to the level your spec needs. Painters get a wall that takes the first coat.</p>
            <ul class="checklist">
              <li>Standard, fire-rated, moisture-resistant, and abuse-resistant board</li>
              <li>Level 4 finish for typical paint and light wall covering</li>
              <li>Level 5 finish for critical lighting and gloss surfaces</li>
              <li>Insulation install coordinated with framing</li>
              <li>Skim coats and patching on tenant improvements</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="acoustical">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="split">
          <div>
            <span class="eyebrow">Acoustical Ceilings</span>
            <h2>Drop ceilings done right the first time.</h2>
            <p>T-bar grid, drywall ceilings, and specialty acoustical work. We coordinate ceiling mounted services with the mechanical, electrical, sprinkler, and lighting trades so cuts line up and tiles drop in without rework.</p>
            <ul class="checklist">
              <li>9/16" and 15/16" T-bar grids in all major finishes</li>
              <li>Acoustical tile selection for office, healthcare, and education</li>
              <li>Custom suspension heights, slopes, and ceiling clouds</li>
              <li>Linear metal, wood, and specialty ceiling systems</li>
              <li>Coordinated integration with HVAC, sprinkler, and lighting</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="img-frame"><img src="/assets/images/suspended-ceiling-installation-calgary-office.jpg" alt="Acoustical T-bar ceiling install in a Calgary commercial space" loading="lazy" /></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="tenant" class="section-dark">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="section-head">
          <span class="eyebrow">Tenant Improvements</span>
          <h2>The trades partner Calgary landlords keep on speed dial.</h2>
          <p class="lead">When a deal closes and the build-out clock starts ticking, you want a contractor who can mobilize, coordinate, and finish without surprises. That's the work we've been doing for forty years.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pillars">
          <article class="pillar" style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);">
            <div class="pillar-icon" style="background: rgba(234,88,12,0.1);" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"/><path d="M9 22V12h6v10"/></svg></div>
            <h3>Office &amp; retail fit-outs</h3>
            <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);">Demising walls, demo, new framing, drywall, and ceilings on suite turnovers and full-floor build-outs.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="pillar" style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);">
            <div class="pillar-icon" style="background: rgba(234,88,12,0.1);" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2H7a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16M3 21h18M9 9h.01M9 13h.01M9 17h.01M15 9h.01M15 13h.01M15 17h.01"/></svg></div>
            <h3>Healthcare &amp; education</h3>
            <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);">Hospital wings, dental clinics, school renovations, and post-secondary buildings with the spec-grade work the inspectors expect.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="pillar" style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);">
            <div class="pillar-icon" style="background: rgba(234,88,12,0.1);" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><path d="M12 7v10M7 12h10"/></svg></div>
            <h3>Institutional &amp; civic</h3>
            <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);">Municipal buildings, libraries, recreation facilities, and the kind of public work that earns repeat invitations to bid.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Base>
